WEBVTT

00:09:28.192 --> 00:09:31.787
with a simple but brilliant idea

00:09:31.811 --> 00:09:37.075
that I first heard from a risk-taking,
dangerous congresswoman from New York

00:09:37.099 --> 00:09:38.813
named Bella Abzug.

00:09:39.700 --> 00:09:42.993
Bella said, "In the 21st century,

00:09:43.017 --> 00:09:46.844
women will change the nature of power

00:09:46.868 --> 00:09:51.289
rather than power changing
the nature of women."

00:09:52.175 --> 00:09:54.094
From the moment I heard that --

00:09:54.118 --> 00:09:55.874
(Applause)

00:09:55.898 --> 00:09:58.949
I thought, "This is our call to action.

00:09:58.973 --> 00:10:01.890
This is our biggest opportunity."